---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CookieConsent from '../components/CookieConsent.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Meet the Founder | Reignite Solutions';
const pageDesc =
  'The story behind Reignite Solutions — why it was started, what problems it exists to solve, and how Alex works with UK organisations to restore clarity, momentum, and results.';
---
<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDesc}>
  <Header />

  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-16 bg-surface text-ink">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-6xl grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent/10 text-accent text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide px-4 py-1 rounded-full mb-5">
            Meet the founder
          </span>
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-extrabold mb-4 leading-tight">
            Alex Hunter.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-ink/70 mb-6 max-w-xl">
            Founder of Reignite Solutions. Obsessed with helping organisations turn good intentions into actual,
            measurable progress — without drowning people in process or jargon.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink/60">
            Based in Ilkley, West Yorkshire. Working with UK teams remotely.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-40 h-40 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-ink/5 shadow-sm p-6 space-y-4 relative z-10">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-ink/50">Why Reignite?</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-display text-ink leading-snug">
            “I kept seeing smart teams stall because nobody had made things clear, simple, and doable.<br>Reignite exists to
            fix that.”
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink/40">
            Clarity first. Momentum always. Results or it doesn’t count.
          </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ORIGIN STORY (DARK) -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-ink text-white">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-6xl space-y-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="h-6 w-1 rounded bg-accent"></span>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white/50">The story</p>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">
            Built after watching good work get stuck.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/75">
            Reignite wasn’t started to chase buzzwords. It was started because too many projects, products, and internal
            initiatives were slowing down — not because the ideas were bad, but because the execution was messy.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/75">
            Alex created Reignite to be the “guiding hand” that organisations can bring in when they need to get moving
            again — calmly, clearly, and with everyone pulling in the same direction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">A practical operator</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/75">
              Less theory, more “here’s how we’ll do it this month”. You get someone who’s actually run work, not just
              commented on it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Champion of clarity</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/75">
              If people don’t understand the plan, it’s not a plan. Alex simplifies language, goals, and ownership.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Partner, not preacher</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/75">
              Works alongside your teams — not hovering above them — to build ways of working that feel natural.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHAT ALEX BELIEVES (LIGHT) -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface text-ink">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-6xl space-y-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="h-6 w-1 rounded bg-accent"></span>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-ink/60">What Alex believes</p>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">
            Progress beats presentation. Every time.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-ink/70">
            The Reignite approach is opinionated — it’s designed for organisations that want visible movement without
            hiring a giant consultancy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-ink/10 p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">1. Start with the outcome</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink/70">
              If we don’t know what we’re trying to change — for customers, teams, or leadership — we stop and define it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-ink/10 p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">2. Make it understandable</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink/70">
              No jargon, no hiding behind process. Everyone should know what’s happening and why.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-ink/10 p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">3. Work with people, not around them</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink/70">
              Real change happens when the people doing the work are involved in shaping it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-ink/10 p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">4. Leave things better than we found them</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink/70">
              Teams should be more confident, more organised, and more self-sufficient at the end of an engagement.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EXPERIENCE / CREDIBILITY (DARK) -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-ink text-white">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-6xl space-y-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="h-6 w-1 rounded bg-accent"></span>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white/50">Experience</p>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">
            Experience across digital, product, and change.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/75">
            Alex has worked with teams where the challenge wasn’t “what should we do?” — it was “how do we get this done
            without burning everyone out?”. That’s the problem Reignite is built to solve.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Leading change</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/75">
              Helping organisations shift how they plan, prioritise, and communicate — so teams can move together.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Supporting product & digital</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/75">
              Working with product, engineering, and ops to make their work more predictable and visible.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-5 space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Partnering with leadership</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/75">
              Giving senior leaders a clear story to tell — and the confidence that the work is actually moving.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PERSONAL / HUMAN BIT (LIGHT) -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface text-ink">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-6xl grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="h-6 w-1 rounded bg-accent"></span>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-ink/60">A human, not a machine</p>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold mb-3">
            Yorkshire base, UK focus.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-ink/70">
            Reignite is deliberately small and hands-on. That means you work directly with Alex — not a junior team who
            didn’t write the proposal. It also means we can move at your pace.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink/80 space-y-1">
            <li>• Located in Ilkley, West Yorkshire</li>
            <li>• Used to working with distributed UK teams</li>
            <li>• Clear, straightforward communication style</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-ink/10 p-6 space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">How to work with Alex</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink/70 space-y-1">
            <li>1. Quick call to understand what’s slowing you down</li>
            <li>2. Light-touch proposal — in plain English</li>
            <li>3. Hands-on engagement to create visible progress</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink/40">
            No hard sell. Just an honest assessment of whether Reignite is the right fit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-ink text-white text-center">
      <div class="container-reignite max-w-4xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold mb-4">
          Want to talk through what you’re trying to move?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-6">
          Share what’s stuck or unclear in your organisation and Alex will outline the simplest way to make progress.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-surface text-ink px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white transition"
        >
          Contact Reignite
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <CookieConsent />
</BaseLayout>
